content:
Can you determine which of the following personality traits does not belong to the 'big five'? 
a) Conscientiousness 
b) Extraversion 
c) Openness 
d) Humility 
e) Agreeableness

The personality trait that does not belong to the 'big five' is:

d) Humility

The "Big Five" personality traits are Conscientiousness, Extraversion, Openness, Agreeableness, and Neuroticism. Humility is not included in this model.
